data.description: Beautiful 3/2 POOL Home wit 2-Car Tandem Garage. This home's floor plan is perfect for entertaining. Tons of windows throughout bring in all the natural light. Spacious home with entry foyer & formal dining room. The living area has an open layout to the kitchen. Roomy dining room has plenty of space to enjoy those family dinners. Home features: insulated attic, dual pain windows, ceiling fans, beautiful vaulted ceilings, laminate wood flooring through out and tiled floors in the kitchen and entry way. Living room has cozy fireplace to enjoy on those cold nights. Don’t miss this perfect starter  in the quiet Spring neighborhood. Easy access to walking trails. Enjoy oversized pool on a sunny day. Just a 30 minute drive to major supermarkets and the cinema, and walking distance to schools, dog park and playground. Only minutes to the freeway and to downtown. 30 minutes to Cynthia pavilion and Woodlands mall !NEVER flooded.
